query:
SELECT m.id as module_id, m.name as module_name, p.id as page_id, p.title as page_title, p.order
FROM modules m
LEFT JOIN pages p ON p.moduleId = m.id
WHERE m.disciplineId = 1
ORDER BY m.order, p.order
LIMIT 50;
